# =============================================================================
# tinyproxy.filter — Claude Code egress allowlist
# =============================================================================
# Domains the container is allowed to reach at runtime.
# tinyproxy uses extended regular expressions (ERE) by default.
# Each line is matched against the full hostname of the request.
#
# Syntax:
#   exact.domain.com      matches only that host
#   \.domain\.com$        matches domain.com and any subdomain
#
# To add a domain temporarily for a session, edit this file and send
# SIGHUP to tinyproxy: kill -HUP $(cat /tmp/claude-sandbox-tinyproxy.pid)
# No container restart needed.
# =============================================================================

# Anthropic API — all Claude Code inference calls
api\.anthropic\.com$

# Claude.ai — OAuth authentication flow
claude\.ai$

# Anthropic Console — API key / Console account auth
platform\.claude\.com$
